high_descs: pick up square frying pan on the left side of the stove top
chill pan inside the fridge, remove frying pan from fridge
walk to face green counter top
put frying pan on the green counter top
anns.task_desc: put a chilled frying pan onto a counter top

high_descs: Walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the oven.
Pick up the metal pan off of the back left burner of the stove.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the metal pan inside then close the door, after a couple second open the fridge back up and remove the pan then close the door.
Turn right and walk towards the oven, then hang a right and walk up to the island.
Put the chilled pan on the island to the right of the sweet potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled metal pan on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the stove to your right.
Pick up the pan on the stove.
Turn around and walk to the fridge to your right.
Place the pan inside the fridge, cool it then remove it.
Turn right and walk to the green table to your right with the pan.
Place the cool pan on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool pan on the table.
